reviewText:
Okay I was sceptical about this cause I have the originals in my room and all I can say is let the dust build up. I am not kidding this is how great the set is now here is what you get

1. The books complete no you don't have to buy a part 2 or something like that

2. Yes it comes with a digital copy of the movie in HD or for Vudu and Flixister Vudu I know is HDX so there

3. Comes with the Book too so if you don't like reading the book or just put it on ipod or whatever yes they give you that

4. Then the DVD oh and the box set which is just so nice heavy but I can read the book while watching it

This set is worth your money get it before it runs out if another comes out I will be sure to buy it
Don't waste your money. You can get 25 animated movies digitally on Google Play for the same price...nope nope... beware

Too many scalpers. I bought the same set from Amazon for $100.
